---
title: Software for community supported agriculture, food co-ops, artisan bakers, vegetable box schemes and local food deliveries
description: Bucky Box, simple to use software for your CSA, Vegetable Box Scheme, Food Co-op, Artisan Bakery or Food Hub to automate orders, billing and delivery logistics
---

.container-fluid{style: "margin-top: -30px"}
  .row.text-center
    #carousel.carousel.slide{"data-ride" => "carousel"}
      .carousel-caption
        .btn-group
          %a.btn.btn-lg.btn-secondary{href: "tour.html", role: "button"} Software for Local Food Enterprises
          %a.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary.sign_up{href: "javascript:void(0)", role: "button"} Sign Up for Free

      %ol.carousel-indicators
        %li.active{"data-target" => "#carousel", "data-slide-to" => "0"}
        %li{"data-target" => "#carousel", "data-slide-to" => "1"}
        %li{"data-target" => "#carousel", "data-slide-to" => "2"}

      .carousel-inner
        - content_for :carousel_item do |params|
          .item{class: ("active" if params.fetch(:active, false))}
            = image_tag params.fetch(:image), class: "img-responsive", alt: params[:image_alt]

        = yield_content :carousel_item, image: "hero-nz-peoples-bread-artisan-bakers.jpg", image_alt: "Bucky Box software helps Artisan Bakers, The Peoples Bread Company", active: true
        = yield_content :carousel_item, image: "hero-au-mpcheap-vegbox-deliveries.jpg", image_alt: "Vegetable box deliveries by MP Cheap Fruit and Veg grew incredibly quickly with Bucky Box software"
        = yield_content :carousel_item, image: "hero-nz-the-local-vegbox-deliveries.jpg", image_alt: "The back office administration is now quick and easy for the Local Veg Box, a UK vegetable box scheme"

      = link_to "#carousel", class: "carousel-control left", "data-slide" => "prev" do
        %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-chevron-left

      = link_to "#carousel", class: "carousel-control right", "data-slide" => "next" do
        %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-chevron-right


.container
  .row.voffset-2
    %h3.text-center Powering Local Food

  #home-powering-local-food
    - content_for :mission do |params|
      .box.col-sm-6{class: ("text-right-sm" if params.fetch(:side) == :right)}
        .panel.panel-default
          .panel-body
            .row
              .col-xs-4.visible-xs
                = image_tag params.fetch(:image), class: "img-responsive"
              - if params.fetch(:side) == :right
                .col-xs-4.hidden-xs
                  = image_tag params.fetch(:image), class: "img-responsive"
              .col-xs-8
                %h4 #{params.fetch(:label)}
                %p #{params.fetch(:description)}
              - if params.fetch(:side) == :left
                .col-xs-4.hidden-xs
                  = image_tag params.fetch(:image), class: "img-responsive"

    .row
      = yield_content :mission, side: :left, image: "i-web-store.png", label: "Web Store", description: "Your customers place single or standing orders through an easy to set up web store."

      = yield_content :mission, side: :right, image: "i-customer-database.png", label: "Customer Database", description: "Each of your customers can track their account balance, status and entire history through the customer database."

    .row.text-center
      .col-md-12.visible-md.visible-lg{style: "margin-top: -70px; margin-bottom: -70px; z-index: 1"}
        = image_tag "i-loop.png"

    .row
      = yield_content :mission, side: :left, image: "i-payments.png", label: "Payments", description: "All manner of payment methods are available, and each payment is reconciled with the customer's account."

      = yield_content :mission, side: :right, image: "i-deliveries.png", label: "Fulfilment", description: "Deliveries and pickups are scheduled, packing lists are generated, and deliveries are reconciled."

  .row.voffset-2
    %h3.text-center Saving your time

  .panel.panel-default.text-center.voffset
    .panel-body
    .row
      .col-md-2.voffset
        %h3 2 days
        .text-muted Spreadsheets
      .col-md-8
        = image_tag "i-time-savings.png", class: "img-responsive"
      .col-md-2.voffset
        %h3 2 hours
        .text-muted Bucky Box
    .row.voffset
      .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
        %p
          A typical food delivery business can spend up to 2 days per week on customer support and business administration.
          With Bucky Box automating the most common tasks, we can get this down to 2 hours per week.

  .row.text-center.voffset-2
    .col-md-4.col-md-offset-4
      %h3 Who uses Bucky Box?
      %p Bucky Box works best for food enterprises selling by recurring subscription directly to customers.

  #home-who-uses-bb
    .row.text-center.voffset
      .operation.col-xs-6.col-sm-4
